For parallel? (lib)


1st: https://github.com/TooBiased/growt

2nd: phmap::parallel_flat_hash_map

-------
API:

 iterator:
   forward/backward/fast

 lambda_each:
   flood_fast/flood_forward/flood_backward


   Similar to fwd/bwd/fast, but it has a starting point and stop propagating
   when the the lambda returns false.


